\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \strokec2 Shellack or Gellack is  a special hybrid nail polish developed by CND (Creative Nail Design). It combines the qualities of regular nail polish and gel polish. Shellac is applied like traditional polish but cured under a UV or LED lamp, which makes it more durable and chip-resistant. It usually lasts about 3/4 weeks with a high-shine finish. You cannot extend the nail with shellack, however, you can build it a little bit (if your nails are flat). Wide range of colours awaits your visit! (We also have a huge selection of coloured  protein base coats - the best ones on the market lately- if you prefer a \'84clean nails\'94 trend.) \
\
Tip: Want your cutticles to stay soft? Ask your therapist about  our shea cutticle oils collection!\outl0\strokewidth0 \
\
